+```markdown
+## Summary
+[Feature name from spec.md]
+
+## Spec Coverage
+[Paste the spec-coverage checklist from the verify run]
+
+## Verification Evidence
+- Test suite: [N] tests, [N] passing, 0 failing
+- Spec coverage: [N/N] requirements verified
